about.author: Timo Homburg
about.comment: Hittite Unicode Dictionary. This dictionary contains Hittite base forms of words and shall be a basis for Natural Language Processing on the Hittite language. The dictionary also features common Sumerograms and Akkadograms which can be found in Hittite.
